{"tid":933583,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[咖啡撚] 到底 咖啡豆 係咩植物?","createTime":"2018-12-08T15:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T03:42:49.000Z","uid":41315,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58395a2e2dfc4fb45cd456352beda616e21b25a7","tid":933583,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jrPFAsm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjrPFAsm.jpg&h=20c287e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgBphFH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgBphFH.jpg&h=078a628d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfHG4kJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfHG4kJ.jpg&h=a649b24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實咖啡<br />\n應該係帶有花香<br />\n莓果類既酸甜味<br />\n又或者帶有堅果既香味<br />\n而唔會有苦味<br />\n<br />\n上面紅色既，係咖啡果實<br />\n即係 咖啡豆既前身<br />\n幻想就咁食落口<br />\n應該都係酸酸甜甜<br />\n味道應該同 車厘子 差唔多<br />\n<br />\n好既咖啡，飲落都會似 果汁<br />\n以往既咖啡豆，烘焙到燶哂<br />\n就好似煎燶既牛扒會苦<br />\n食落味道似炭<br />\n<br />\n咖啡豆以前都係烘都燶哂<br />\n所以飲落會似炭水<br />\n<br />\n精品咖啡，就好似靚牛扒，煎返7成熟<br />\n飲落鮮甜甘潤，酸甜適中<br />\n<br />\n其實我係黎推廣精品咖啡<br />\n歡迎入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a89a9af516e7b9e7c055999aab2770db64975e","tid":933583,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"見巴打開post 搭單一問<br />\n間Dog99啲嘢得唔得？我見佢開24想去試下"},{"pid":"67af1e816c8234b1b10b1ecef6d4631910ab44db","tid":933583,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a89a9af516e7b9e7c055999aab2770db64975e","tid":933583,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"見巴打開post 搭單一問<br />\n